<title type="html"><![CDATA[konami justifier=super scope?]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=3652&amp;p=32843#p32843"><![CDATA[
I have a Super Scope. But I don't have like 6 AA batteries handy. But I can assure you that only games that say Super Scope will work with it. And the only game I know of that uses a "standard" Lightgun is Lethal Enforcers which had the Justifier.<br /><br />It is important to point out that the Super Scope has more buttons, turbo fire, and a MUCH bigger lens which makes it ALOT more accurate than most lightguns. Not to mention the very handy scope sight.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=1726">MottZilla</a> — Sun Apr 20, 2008 3:27 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
