OK, hopefully someone here will know the answer to my question since I have zero replies on like 4 or 5 other forums (for some weeks now).<br /><br />here is the question: Will the Konami Justifier work with Super Scope compatible games?<br /><br />The reason I am asking is because I have the konami justifier pistols (blue and rare red/orange) and they work great and I have no intention of owning that behemoth Super Scope battery munching POS.  That said, there are a few games that are fun to play with a light gun like T2: the Arcade Game, Battleclash, Super Scope 6, etc. and if I could play them with a justifier I would pick them up.  I figure SOMEONE on here must either own a justifier or know one way or another.  The justifier only has a trigger and Start button, so I don't know if that matters since I haven't used a super scope in like 15 years and I don't remember what buttons it had.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=3414">17daysolderthannes</a> — Sat Oct 27, 2007 6:41 pm</p><hr />
